text LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_EventScript_LittleGirlHaveCase {
    format("Yippee!\p The lady at the reception counter gave me a case for {POKEBLOCK}S!$ Make {POKEBLOCK}S and put them in there.\p When you make a {POKEBLOCK}, everyone has to put in a different BERRY.$ Congratulations!\p I did a painting of your POKéMON to commemorate its victory…\p Well, your POKéMON's appeals were so fantastic, it spurred me into\l painting better than I usually do.\l Look, see?$ What do you think? I'm confident in what I've done, but do you like it?\p A work of this caliber, it wouldn't look out of place in an art museum.\p Huh? An art museum really is looking for paintings?\p Do you think I should take this there?$ What, really? Then, sure, I will take this painting there right now.\p I'll give it a proper title, too.\p I hope they'll like it and consider exhibiting this.\p Please check if they did accept this. Thank you!$ Oh, that's right!\p As a memento of me painting your POKéMON, please take this.$ {PLAYER} received a RIBBON.$ {PLAYER} put the RIBBON on {STR_VAR_1}.$ Okay, see you!$ Oh… Then, I guess I'll just take this home with me…\p But, you know, I would like to take this to the art museum… Okay?$ Oh, fine, that's the way it is. I will hang this in my own house.\p I'll just have to try harder next time. Well, be seeing you.$ Hoo, boy… Master Rank CONTESTS, here I come.\p The world will know that my dearest POKéMON is the cutest being in all\l existence. The time has come!\l Uheheheh.$ You can see a whole variety of POKéMON here.\p That's why I make this place a regular part of my daily stroll.$ Wow, coming out to a CONTEST is a feast for these eyes!\p Would you look at all the POKéMON that just scream to be painted?$ The TOUGHNESS CONTEST is like extreme, man!\p Those muscular appeals… Cascading sweat… I swoon!$ Day in and day out, I lavished my care on this POKéMON.\p Its condition is peaking. Today, victory is mine!$ I made {POKEBLOCK}S with Mom, Dad, and Big Sister. They turned out great!\p I bet you can make smoother, better {POKEBLOCK}S if you have more people.")
}

